ricoh-spc240sf-driver (1.0.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release.
  * Native C CUPS filter (rastertoddst) producing the DDST stream
    consumed by the Ricoh Aficio SP C240SF.
  * Multi-threaded JBIG encoding of the four CMYK planes per band.
  * PPD with A4/Letter/Legal/A5/B5/B6/A6/Executive/envelopes/postcard,
    duplex, two paper trays, plain/thick/thin/recycled media.
  * udev rule auto-registers the printer in CUPS on USB plug.

 -- Ricoh SP C240SF Linux project <noreply@example.com>  Wed, 20 May 2026 18:00:00 +0000
